text: Anna Krūmiņa (born 31 January 1999) is a Latvian footballer who plays as a defender and has appeared for the Latvia women's national team. ==Career== Krūmiņa has been capped for the Latvia national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Latvian women's footballers Category:Latvia women's international footballers Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Rīgas FS players
